&lt;li&gt;Build and manage custom registration sites and event apps that capture travel requirements and customized scheduling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel to lead on-site execution, manage teams and partners, and represent Bluefish with professionalism and authenticity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage logistical requirements for planning, staging, and shipping of tradeshow properties, products, and supporting materials.&lt;/li&gt;
