&lt;li&gt;Establish staffing requirements, secure approvals, and recruit employees to support events as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain clear communication with internal and external stakeholders through detailed briefs and regular planning updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Content &amp;amp; Programming&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
