&lt;li&gt;Define objectives, messaging, and audience generation strategies for each event, including email campaigns, speaker plans, collateral, and registration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research and evaluate potential guest speakers and external voices to elevate programming.&lt;/li&gt;
