&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Position:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Bluefish is looking for a technically strong, customer-facing Senior Customer AI Engineer to support&amp;nbsp;enterprise customers throughout their AI Marketing efforts—from implementation and integration through&amp;nbsp;optimization and expansion. This role sits at the intersection of account management, AI solutioning, and&amp;nbsp;technical delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You will act as a trusted technical partner for customers, ensuring smooth transitions from sales to&amp;nbsp;account ownership, supporting complex integrations, and helping customers unlock measurable value&amp;nbsp;from Bluefish’s AI platform. The ideal candidate is equally comfortable discussing APIs and data pipelines&amp;nbsp;as they are explaining AI-driven outcomes to non-technical stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
