&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Support the technical relationship for assigned customer accounts, serving as the primary point of contact for integrations, configurations, and advanced technical questions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Support RFP and RFI responses, expanding technical sections and helping streamline internal processes for scale and consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Guide and support customer integrations, including APIs, data feeds, product catalogs, and other platform dependencies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Design and support custom technical solutions, such as dashboards, data exports, and bespoke agents workflows tailored to customer needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Partner with customers on complex optimization measurement, automation, and performance validation to ensure measurable business impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Collaborate closely with product, engineering, sales, and customer success to surface customer feedback and inform roadmap priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Help identify opportunities for account expansion and deeper platform adoption through technical use cases and optimization strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
