&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Minimum of 5+ years of experience in a Technical Account Manager, Solutions Engineer, Customer Engineer, or similar client-facing technical role, ideally in SaaS, AI, or marketing technology.&lt;/li&gt;
