&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Position:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bluefish is on the cutting edge of AI-powered SaaS, helping brands understand their performance and optimization in the new AI funnel. As part of our&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Marketing Services team&lt;/strong&gt;, we’re looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Customer AI Researcher&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to lead the charge in uncovering how AI models perceive, rank, and recommend the world’s leading brands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will be the technical engine of our research arm. You aren&#39;t just looking at data; you are conducting sophisticated experiments to understand the mechanics of the AI-powered internet. You will bridge the gap between abstract marketing questions and hard technical evidence, ensuring every insight we deliver is defensible, credible, and actionable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Doing:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Implementation &amp;amp; Ownership&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– Own the end-to-end technical research stack, including platform specifications, configurations, advanced prompt engineering, custom queries, and the architecture of client-facing dashboards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thought Leadership &amp;amp; Industry Insight&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– Generate high-impact thought leadership ideas by synthesizing industry trends, internal best practices, and deep-dive platform knowledge into fresh perspectives for the market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Measurement Scoping &amp;amp; Analysis&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– Translate strategic briefs into rigorous data requirements. You will define the boundaries of our research by scoping what can be captured within the platform versus what requires bespoke external analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Editorial &amp;amp; Data Credibility&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– Partner closely with the Editorial Director to co-author content briefs, ensuring that all data-driven narratives are technically sound, defensible, and meet the highest standards of credibility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Synthesis &amp;amp; Insights&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– Responsible for delivering clean, structured datasets and distilling them into the &quot;top 3&quot; most actionable insights that drive immediate value for our clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Excellence &amp;amp; Scalability&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– Build and maintain the &quot;Research Playbook.&quot; You will create scalable processes that allow our team to conduct deep-dive audits for clients faster and with higher precision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Strategy Partnership&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– Act as a critical technical bridge, providing our Product and Engineering teams in Berlin with direct evidence from the field on platform performance and emerging AI model behaviors.&lt;/li&gt;
