&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Mastery&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– Hands-on experience with LLM configurations and prompt engineering. You are comfortable building complex queries and designing intuitive BI dashboards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analytic Rigor&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– You have a proven ability to manage large datasets and the &quot;detective&quot; mindset required to find patterns in the noise of AI-generated responses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Translation&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– You can take a high-level marketing question and break it down into a technical measurement plan with clear &quot;can/cannot&quot; parameters.&lt;/li&gt;
