&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Position&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bluefish is seeking an exceptional product leader with the rare ability to own every aspect of the product lifecycle — from high-level strategy to detailed execution — while building and leading a world-class product organization. The VP of Product will set the vision and direction for our entire product portfolio, serving as both a strategic executive and a hands-on leader who can inspire a team while rolling up their sleeves when it matters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role spans all levels of leadership — from defining broad product vision and company strategy to developing detailed specs and guiding implementation. As both a strategic driver and an empowering manager, you will be the executive force behind our product&#39;s success, responsible for aligning the organization around customer needs and ensuring we&#39;re building the right solutions to solve real problems at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must be comfortable operating at the executive level while remaining grounded in product craft — engaging directly with the board and leadership on strategy, while also diving deep with engineering, design, and go-to-market teams. You will thrive navigating an ambiguous and rapidly evolving AI marketing landscape, and you know how to build and scale a product organization from an early stage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate has experience scaling products and teams in both startup and enterprise environments, is deeply customer-oriented, and is motivated by the challenge of building something category-defining from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
