&lt;li&gt;Define and champion a compelling product vision and multi-year roadmap that aligns with company strategy, market opportunity, and customer needs — and rally the organization around it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, lead, and mentor a high-performing product team, establishing best practices, processes, and a culture of customer obsession and rigorous execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and drive end-to-end product strategy across the full portfolio, ensuring each initiative has a clear vision, measurable outcomes, and cross-functional alignment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a key member of the executive team, contributing to company strategy, fundraising narratives, board communications, and organizational decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spot macro trends, evaluate competitive landscapes, and translate insights into differentiated product strategies that position Bluefish as a market leader.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply rigor to deeply understand customer needs and pain points at scale. Identify and prioritize features and bets that deliver maximum value and create sustainable competitive advantage.&lt;/li&gt;
