&lt;li&gt;Define and monitor product success metrics, evaluate ROI, and create accountability frameworks that connect product outcomes to business results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the product externally — with key customers, partners, analysts, and the press — as a credible and inspiring spokesperson for Bluefish&#39;s vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
